reviews:

Just wish the neck piece was somehow different! Also sewed two hair elastics for each arm so that the wings would follow my movement - they just come with two small elastics for fingers attached!

review_title: Wings for Pride and an extra layer of sun protection
reviews: Ordered for Pride, my arms are a bit long for the thumb loops, but will just tie them to my wrists. Good quality and much better than expected. Definitely recommend, brilliant design and vivid colours.
product_name: Halloween Ladies Fairy Nymph Elf Soft Fabric Butterfly Wings Costume Accessory

reviews: The fabric is only printed on the outside, but it's a soft, thick material, not some cheap paper thin stuff. The collar is stretchy and also has velcro to adjust. The corners of the velcro can scratch a bit at the neck if they aren't lined up well. The tip of the wings also have a finger loop so you don't have to constantly hold them. Colours are incredibly vibrant, love this item!
product_name: Halloween Ladies Fairy Nymph Elf Soft Fabric Butterfly Wings Costume Accessory

reviews: It's just ok. It's plenty long enough for an adult but the wings aren't attached together at the back so you can't see them when your arms are down. Also the print is only on the back so from the front you don't see the pattern. I wouldn't have bought them if I knew that. I've bought kids wings in the past that were printed both sides, one large shaped piece of fabric, and fit with elastics on the shoulders like a backpack strap instead of around the neck. Those are way better. I wouldn't buy these again.
product_name: Halloween Ladies Fairy Nymph Elf Soft Fabric Butterfly Wings Costume Accessory

reviews: The "butterfly rose" wings are not purple like the photo implies. It is a very bright pink. The choice of material for the choker part is an odd jewel pattern that does not fit with the wings. A plain black would have been a better choice. I am 5'4" and I could not stretch my arms out straight if I had the finger loops on. The colour on the front is VERY light but the back is quite vibrant. The seams are quite flimsy and I don't see these wings lasting long.
product_name: Halloween Ladies Fairy Nymph Elf Soft Fabric Butterfly Wings Costume Accessory

reviews:
Delivery was amazing, 2 days.
Colors nice and vibrant, wish some color was on the reverse side a bit as quite white and flows while walking. As I was taking it out of the shipping bag, one finger strap fell off...so while I’m sewing that back on I think I’ll tack the back together as I found the entire wing tends to fall over the shoulder when wearing, or perhaps I’ll tack near the back of the shirt I plan to wear with it. Neck elastic comfortable, not tight at all, has a front Velcro closure. For $26 with shipping it is an ok buy for my Halloween costume.
product_name: Halloween Ladies Fairy Nymph Elf Soft Fabric Butterfly Wings Costume Accessory

reviews: I wanted it to arrive on time so I could use it for Halloween. I asked for the request and they replied to me very quickly. I am a dancer and a performer, and I used this butterfly costume for my halloween dance gig. Everyone loved it!! The inside of the fabric is a bit plain so I added some shiny stickers to be extra shiny! I would recommend this to anyone!
product_name: Halloween Ladies Fairy Nymph Elf Soft Fabric Butterfly Wings Costume Accessory

review_title: My daughter was pleased with this costume!
reviews:
The package came within two days as promised.
My daughter was pleased with this butterfly costume. She said the neck part velcro was bothering her a little but she just wrapped a bandana around it and didn’t find it too bothersome afterwards. One finger elastic broke off immediately. I had to sew it back on and reinforced the other one. I also sewed the middle part on the back.
My daughter stands at 5’1” so you can see the length. It was not an issue at all. Overall she was pleased with this costume as it was pretty and comfortable enough for her to wear in school the whole halloween day.
